name: autoai-phys-validator
description: Validation-driven machine learning framework where scientific constraints act as adaptive validators rather than fixed physics losses. Demonstrated on a climate downscaling example to contrast against PINN-style constraint enforcement

name: moa
description: MOA is an open source framework for Big Data stream mining. It includes a collection of machine learning algorithms (classification, regression, clustering, outlier detection, concept drift detection and recommender systems) and tools for evaluation.
